      },
      "dcterms:description": "Default baseline segmentation model (blla) bundled with Kraken 5.2.5 (released 2024-05-24, commit 31f195ea5aa2276d70cc7bdc1de0a52fc166b51a). Used for automatic detection of text line baselines in manuscript images prior to manual correction.",
      "ddi-cdi:hasRole": [
